N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 149.5 - Procedure in an adolescent diversion part

State Regulations

Each action or proceeding transferred from
a local criminal court to the Supreme Court or County Court and referred for
disposition to an adolescent diversion part thereof shall be subject to the
same substantive and procedural law as would have applied had there been no
transfer. Notes
